---
title: Coconut Fish Curry with coriander and lemon
description: Fish curry is a popular genre of dish in Indian cuisine which can take many different forms. The creaminess in this particular recipe comes in the form of coconut milk, which also helps to temper the mild spices in this dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF211008_R210_W47_FR_RNL0963-9_MB_Main_less_red__high-4794e888.jpg
